Alice-In-Chains-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Alice-In-Chains-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Alice-In-Chains-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Alice-In-Chains-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Alice-In-Chains-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice In Chains</a>发行了重新发行的“Jar Of Flies”黑胶唱片，里面压着真正的死苍蝇。</p><p>为了庆祝乐队的第三张录音室 EP，他们与 Romanus Records 合作制作了限量版透明黑胶唱片，光盘上压有大量死苍蝇。仅生产了 150 件，零售价为每件 100 美元（79 英镑）。不幸的是，罕见的压制已售罄。</p><p>这并不是黑胶唱片公司第一次在压制过程中做出奇怪的事情。他们最近为 Pat &amp; The Pissers 制作了一个充满蛆虫的黑胶唱片。</p><p> Romanus 的 Chris Banta 在社交媒体上透露，“实际上很难找到真正的死苍蝇”。克里斯补充道：“绝对标志性的乐队、专辑等等。视频和更多幕后内容即将推出！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2ioE5Vue6A/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http